    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car shows noticeable interior wear and some minor exterior scuffs and dings. It has been regularly serviced, but prospective buyers should anticipate some upcoming maintenance items typical for its age and mileage. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 20500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
